freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: Increased muscle pain mainly in both shoulders and neck, Took 2 Motrin several times a day for 2 days and counting. increased fatigue. Not sleeping well.

freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: Over the last week and today I have experienced several short duration sharp pain in my right leg lasting less than 3 seconds with no redness and no swelling. In addition I have had several muscle cramps in the same right leg.

Seem to have mucus in back of throat causing clearing of throat. Not sure if this is allergy or reaction from 2nd shot. I have had this before and have taken a Zyrtec. So I took Zyrtec earlier today and it seemed to help.
